{"tid":1874563,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續踢爆前國難員工講大話","createTime":"2020-02-11T09:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T17:25:39.000Z","uid":115986,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab2aec943dc902b58334b90d0979a7031f6296e","tid":1874563,"uid":115986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:21:07.000Z","msg":"話說S小姐蔡女士，一直抹黑李先生係中大理大一役中完全無幫手，我報料人當堂嚇一跳，然後就得啖笑。<br />\n<br />\n呢班人cap咗李生講悔氣說話，以為佢哋有幾清高啦，原來都係有咁講。呢班人為咗抹黑，可以不擇手段，事實上個夢都唔乸係咁。蔡女士堅稱佢派嘅貨唔係國難五金嘅貨，係中大理大嘅黑騎同眼罩唔通從天而降？李生不單止係夢入面有派貨，原來仲幫蔡女士同黨(cap)派嘅貨埋單，換言之，蔡女士聲稱自行購買嘅貨原來係李生畀錢。<br />\n<br />\n蔡女士講嘅野已經再無可信度，只係一班被踢爆偷貨發老脾惡意中傷李生。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXRKyog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXRKyog.jpg&h=57bd88e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2RoMMJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2RoMMJg.jpg&h=cb1cbd41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gHUVBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gHUVBC.jpg&h=d5b1eaef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yzr6MJh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzr6MJh.jpg&h=7710ba14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dop4yoi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDop4yoi.jpg&h=def32184&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7239caf854e43bee95fad83c1e2727f4e36303f1","tid":1874563,"uid":309558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"冇人睬你吖國難打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}